  p.mb--0 #[sup 1] The complex navigation system can either be a menu, a responsive menu-menubar or a non-responsive menubar.
  
  p.mb--0 #[sup 2] Complex menubars are #[a(href="#components-activator") Activator] components.
  
  p #[sup 3] Complex menubar controls also have optional modifier classes #[code .menubar__ctrl--left] or #[code .menubar__ctrl--right].
  
  h3 Collapsed Menubar Control
    
  p Codebase has no styling for the menubar control &ndash; you are at liberty to do whatever you like. Text or icon. Navicon ("hamburger") or no navicon.
    
